fields.description: Westrock Coffee and Rwanda Trading Company work together to provide our customers with a vertically integrated coffee supply chain. We develop blends, products, and brands for a range of clients. We import and roast coffee from around the world, and we produce and export coffee from East Africa through our Rwanda Trading Company subsidiary.
